        <member name="P:nanoFramework.AtomMatrix.AtomMatrix.InfraredLedSettings">
            <summary>
            Gets the infrared led settings.
            </summary>
            <remarks>
            All changes made to <see cref="P:nanoFramework.AtomMatrix.AtomMatrix.InfraredLedSettings"/> are ignored once the <see cref="P:nanoFramework.AtomMatrix.AtomMatrix.InfraredLed"/> is initialized.
            To make additional updates after the infrared channel is initialized, use the properties in <see cref="P:nanoFramework.AtomMatrix.AtomMatrix.InfraredLed"/>.
            Disposing of <see cref="P:nanoFramework.AtomMatrix.AtomMatrix.InfraredLed"/> will free the channel and all changes made to <see cref="P:nanoFramework.AtomMatrix.AtomMatrix.InfraredLedSettings"/> will take effect when <see cref="P:nanoFramework.AtomMatrix.AtomMatrix.InfraredLed"/> is initialized again.
            </remarks>
